{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "###### Example_agyro_coeff.py"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from pyrfu import pyrf\n",
    "from pyrfu import mms\n",
    "from pyrfu import plot as pltrf\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Time interval"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "Tint = [\"2019-09-14T07:54:00.000\",\"2019-09-14T08:11:00.000\"]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Spacecraft index"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ic = 1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Load magnetic field and electron pressure tensor"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Loading mms1_fgm_b_gse_srvy_l2...\n",
      "Loading mms1_des_prestensor_gse_fast...\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "Bxyz = mms.get_data(\"B_gse_fgm_srvy_l2\",Tint,ic)\n",
    "Pexyz = mms.get_data(\"Pe_gse_fpi_fast_l2\",Tint,ic)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Rotate pressure tensor to field aligned coordinates"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "notice Transforming tensor into field-aligned coordinates.\n",
      "notice : Rotating tensor so perpendicular diagonal components are equal.\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "/usr/local/lib/python3.7/site-packages/pyrfu/pyrf/resample.py:153: UserWarning: Using averages in resamp\n",
      "  warnings.warn(\"Using averages in resamp\",UserWarning)\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "Pexyzfac = pyrf.rotate_tensor(Pexyz,\"fac\",Bxyz,\"pp\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Compute agyrotropy coefficient"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "Qe = pyrf.agyro_coeff(Pexyzfac)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,sharex=True)\n",
    "pltrf.plot_line(axs[0],Bxyz)\n",
    "pltrf.plot_line(axs[1],np.sqrt(Qe))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  }
